\section{Inline book references}

It is also possible to make inline links to a book such as \booklink{978-1853267802},
using either its \caps{ISBN-10} or its \caps{ISBN-13}.  You may also include a rating
and a custom title when referencing the book; for example: \booklink<5>{1853267805}{Darwin's
\emph{The Origin of Species}}.


